{"title":"雪花与春花","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":4,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪花与春花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大会堂外，飘着雪花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大会堂内，开着春花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外面是雪花的银海；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里面是春花的云霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪花把改革和开放的信息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒向祖国大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒向海角天涯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春花把各族人民绮丽的憧憬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组合成新的蓝图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组合成新的彩画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪花与春花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽是偶然在这里会晤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春花和雪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却年年要在这里对话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1988年3月下旬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写于人代会上"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}